			"value": "<p>Slicing Blow is a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.hW3DmOPgBpa7lGU8]{Precision Attack}.</p><p><strong>Alternative Sneak Attack</strong> - 1 Creature</p><p>You can transform your sneak attack into an ability that gashes and bleeds your target.</p><ul><li><p><strong>On Hit:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.8Ctt1vOsZuKXxAIN]{Sneak Attack} damage (always &amp;reference[slashing] damage). If your target has blood, they are &amp;Reference[drained] a number of hit points equal to the sneak attack damage you deal. This drained effect lasts until the target finishes a long rest.</p></li></ul>",
